# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok finnish telecommunications company sonera corp. has sold ##.# percent of its stake in voicestream wireless corp. , or #.# million shares , to deutsche telekom ag for about $ ###.# million in a move to reduce the company 's debt .
# ::alignments
(s / sell-01
      :ARG0 (c / company
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Sonera"
                  :op2 "Corp.")
            :mod (c2 / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Finland"))
            :mod (t / telecommunication))
      :ARG1 (o / or
            :op1 (p / percent
                  :quant-of (s2 / stake
                        :poss c
                        :mod (c3 / company
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Vanderestream"
                                    :op2 "Wireless"
                                    :op3 "Corp."))))
            :op2 (s3 / share
                  :quant 1000000))
      :ARG2 (c4 / company
            :name (n4 / name
                  :op1 "Deutsche"
                  :op2 "Telekom"
                  :op3 "Ag"))
      :ARG3 (a / about
            :op1 (m / monetary-quantity
                  :quant 1000000
                  :unit (d / dollar)))
      :ARG1-of (m2 / move-02
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG2 (r / reduce-01
                  :ARG0 c
                  :ARG1 (d2 / debt
                        :poss c))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the foreign ministry denied a report that a british navy landing on a spanish beach next to gibraltar _ which britain said was a mistake _ had been an intentional ploy to torpedo negotiations on the future of the rock .
# ::alignments
(d / deny-01
      :ARG0 (g / government-organization
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Foreign"
                  :op2 "Ministry"))
      :ARG1 (r / report-01
            :ARG1 (p / ploy
                  :ARG1-of (ii / intend-01)
                  :domain (l / land-01
                        :ARG0 (n2 / navy
                              :mod (c / country
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Great"
                                          :op2 "Britain")))
                        :location (b / beach
                              :mod (c2 / country
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "Spain"))
                              :location (n5 / next-to
                                    :op1 (t / territory
                                          :name (n6 / name
                                                :op1 "Gibraltar"))))
                        :ARG1-of (m / mistake-02
                              :ARG0 c
                              :ARG1-of (s / say-01
                                    :ARG0 c)))
                  :domain l)))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok in early #### , as talk of war in europe clouded the horizon and hard economic times gripped the nation , a group of business and political leaders in this northern wyoming city hatched an audacious , if not quite ridiculous , plan to break off huge chunks of wyoming , south dakota and montana and form a new state .
# ::alignments
(h / hatch-01
      :ARG0 (g / group
            :consist-of (a / and
                  :op1 (p / person
                        :ARG0-of (l / lead-02
                              :ARG1 (b / business)))
                  :op2 (p2 / person
                        :ARG0-of (l2 / lead-02
                              :ARG1 (p3 / politics))))
            :location (c / city
                  :location (n / north
                        :part-of (s / state
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Wyoming")))
                  :mod (t / this)))
      :ARG1 (p4 / plan-01
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (b2 / break-off-04
                        :ARG1 (c2 / chunk-01
                              :ARG1 (a3 / and
                                    :op1 s
                                    :op2 (s2 / south
                                          :part-of (d / district
                                                :name (n3 / name
                                                      :op1 "Dakota"))
                                          :op3 (s3 / state
                                                :name (n4 / name
                                                      :op1 "Montana")))
                                    :mod (h2 / huge))))
                  :op2 (f / form-01
                        :ARG1 (s4 / state
                              :ARG1-of (n5 / new-01))))
            :mod (a4 / audacious)
            :ARG1-of (r / ridiculous-02
                  :polarity -
                  :degree (q / quite)))
      :time (e / early)
      :time (a5 / and
            :op1 (c3 / cloud-01
                  :ARG0 (t2 / talk-01
                        :ARG1 (w / war-01)
                        :location (c4 / continent
                              :name (n6 / name
                                    :op1 "Europe")))
                  :ARG1 (h3 / horizon))
            :op2 (g2 / grip-01
                  :ARG0 (t3 / time
                        :ARG1-of (h4 / hard-04)
                        :mod (e2 / economy))
                  :ARG1 (n7 / nation))))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok fidelity investments said yesterday that its magellan fund probably wo n't have any year-end distribution , contrary to the company 's previous estimate that the nation 's largest mutual fund would pay out $ #.## per share in december .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (t / thing
            :ARG1-of (ii / invest-01
                  :ARG0 (c / company
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Fidelity"))))
      :ARG1 (p / probable
            :domain (d / distribute-01
                  :polarity -
                  :ARG1 (f / fund
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Magellan")
                        :poss c)
                  :time (e / end
                        :mod (y / year))
                  :ARG1-of (c2 / contrary-01
                        :ARG2 (e2 / estimate-01
                              :ARG0 (c3 / company)
                              :ARG1 (p2 / pay-out-03
                                    :ARG0 (f2 / fund
                                          :mod (m / mutual)
                                          :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                                                :ARG2 (l / large)
                                                :ARG3 (m2 / most)
                                                :ARG5 (f3 / fund
                                                      :poss (n3 / nation))))
                                    :ARG1 (r / rate-entity-91
                                          :ARG1 (m3 / monetary-quantity
                                                :quant 1000000000
                                                :unit (d2 / dollar))
                                          :ARG2 (s2 / share)
                                          :time (d3 / date-entity
                                                :month 12)))
                              :time (p3 / previous)))))
      :time (y2 / yesterday))

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok olympic ###-meter champion christine ohuruogu withdrew injured from england 's track and field team on tuesday for the new delhi commonwealth games due to injury .
# ::alignments
(w / withdraw-01
      :ARG1 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Christine"
                  :op2 "Ohuruogu")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (w2 / world-region
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Great"
                              :op2 "Britain"))
                  :ARG2 (c / champion
                        :mod (d / distance-quantity
                              :quant 1
                              :unit (m / meter)))))
      :ARG2 (t / team
            :poss (c2 / country
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "England"))
            :mod (t2 / track)
            :mod (f / field))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (t3 / tuesday))
      :ARG1-of (c3 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (ii / injure-01)
            :ARG1 w)
      :ARG0 ii)

            :ARG0 (ii / italy)
            :ARG1 (d / drop-01

                        :ARG1-of (g / gross-03)
                        :mod (d2 / domestic))
                  :ARG2 (p2 / percentage-entity
                        :value 1)))

            :weekday (m / monday)))

# ::id 6 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok japanese share prices fell #.## percent tuesday morning as industrial output data came in lower than expected , dealers said .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (d / deal-01))
      :ARG1 (f / fall-01
            :ARG1 (p2 / price-01
                  :ARG1 (s2 / share
                        :mod (c / country
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Japan"))))
            :ARG2 (p3 / percentage-entity
                  :value ".##")
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / tuesday)
                  :dayperiod (m / morning))
            :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (c3 / come-01
                        :ARG1 (d3 / data
                              :topic (o / output
                                    :mod (ii / industry)))
                        :manner (l / low-04
                              :ARG2-of (h / have-degree-91
                                    :ARG1 d3
                                    :ARG3 (m2 / more)
                                    :ARG4 (e / expect-01)))))))

# ::id 9 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

            :mod (m2 / massive)

                              :op1 "Huangpu")
                        :poss c)

                        :ARG0 r

                              :ARG0-of (t2 / tour-01))

                                                :op1 "Victoria")
